Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人在三尾的腹中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些怪胎 還真像小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺心情舒暢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恍若重生一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前筋疲力盡的感覺也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得力量在源源不斷地湧出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要從木葉的手中奪回幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 四眼君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以目前的狀態而言 我們絕不會輸給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好好表現一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然並不抱太大的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此話當真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按幽鬼丸所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶遁忍者紅蓮還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.48,0:01:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人和紅蓮一起被三尾吞入腹中了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我們如此搜索都毫無蹤跡來看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此言的確不虛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼這麼肯定紅蓮沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是紅蓮姐給我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果紅蓮姐出事的話 這個也會破裂的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這也只能證明紅蓮平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人的安危依舊不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 誰也不知道三尾的腹中會發生些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便都平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但鳴人還是會和晶遁忍者遭遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人很可能會大戰一番 以決雌雄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…鳴人會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在下定論毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能相信他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要找到三尾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以試試
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能找到三尾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然無法確切地知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能隱約感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可即便找到三尾 下面又該如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再進行一次封印術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣吧 先嘗試在這段時間裡營救鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在三尾出現的地點集合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和 為防找到鳴人的同時撞上紅蓮 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和志乃同行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井在上空伺機行事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其餘人員警戒四周
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是兜 天知道他會搞什麼小動作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也要多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃 差不多該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 我們封印班就緊隨在最後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量在不刺激三尾的狀態下 悄悄潛行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擺了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙了啊…這種數量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那種大傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你這身體狀態想怎麼打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說我們能逃去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是走投無路…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶遁.六角手裡劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 完全沒用嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊我先擋著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你伺機逃走吧 知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到我背上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的自尊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在意那些俗事的場合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡 放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道小櫻她們進展是否順利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:08:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人要是平安無事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 肯定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是一個讓我想要與之認真較量的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是敵人大駕光臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好 正是我熱血沸騰的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將對鳴人的思念寄托在這拳頭之上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你能發現我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便消除了蹤跡和氣味 但那股殺氣是無法隱匿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸過一次的手下敗將休想贏我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少狗眼看人低了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經脫胎換骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔煙丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就無法接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要比炮彈量的話 我可不會輸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的苦無都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現身吧 煙龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了 就在這下面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 封印班 準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮姐他們正在找尋出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能從外部打開的話 就能變成出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 看來有必要先調查一下湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山茶花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集多點山茶花過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山茶花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我要問的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:10:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你現在去了西天也取不到西經來救我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是在依賴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你的傷勢如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准碰我 等離開了這裡 你我就是敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你啦 不過我是不會把幽鬼丸交給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼如此執著於幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是已經說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有何隱情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所跟隨的大蛇丸是個大壞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你肯定也是被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟那傢伙一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 你和大蛇丸絕非是幽鬼丸的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去前方稍作偵查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身偵察不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 看起來相當深呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 難道又是那些傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊 為什麼會出現在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有心裡話想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是三尾之霧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這霧能將人內心深處的弱點幻化並顯現出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我進去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也將要面對這些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是您…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對您做了無可挽回的錯事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能得到您的原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便現在已經毫無意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是即便賭上性命 我也會誓死守護您的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 你可是有歸宿的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開 快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所見到的都是幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是見到宇智波佐助了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道佐助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大蛇丸大人那遇見過 是個恐怖的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙沒事吧 還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要問這些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我們的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對要將他帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴佐助 他還有著歸宿所在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當真如此想帶回宇智波佐助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真是個白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由分說地想去幫助那個佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼可笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未見過你這樣的白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 突然間…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得我肚子疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是幽鬼丸所說的通往異世界的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之 只要捅破那層膜 就能製造出出口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 霧突然間…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說向外飄散了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下真是走投無路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 又來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是些糾纏不清的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我回來 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 有件事我必須告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 在這節骨眼上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸的母親不是死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手正是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 為了建立音忍村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人命令我去襲擊幽鬼丸的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 精疲力竭的我在那裡倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她卻救了身為敵人的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧 趁我現在還能當沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要背叛我嗎 紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我卻…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心為了得到大蛇丸大人的認可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而將她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將那時的記憶和感情封印了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻在跟幽鬼丸相遇後全部甦醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才對幽鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給幽鬼丸的心靈造成無以彌補傷害的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有資格去保護那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 現在即便拼上性命也要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要給我活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些話真夠肉麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管以前發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你已經脫胎換骨了 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:18:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山茶花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在為我們引路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你死在這的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一木葉的封印成功的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人未來的戰鬥力將會有很大的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要避免那樣的事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是捨棄幽鬼丸這顆棋子 也是情非得已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拼盡全力去攪亂木葉的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 咒印的逆襲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來收錄的場景是24小時以內
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛入敵人據點的驚險片段
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話筒不出聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 大和隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇本不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又給忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是第二回了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.75,0:22:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 今天可是絕不能犯錯的場合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以為防萬一 還做了V檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂V檢查 就是一邊觀看一邊演練台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來木葉的上忍也墮落了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…也不是這麼回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太遜了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.73,0:22:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算是看錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.14,0:22:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.06,0:22:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 不要說這種話了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了 我的借給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還被塗得亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.72,0:23:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪 饒了我吧
